message: Rule applicable: normalise_associative_commutative ([("Base", 8400)]), to expression: Sum([a, Sum([b, Sum([c, d])]), e]), resulting in: Sum([a, b, c, d, e])
Rule applicable: sum_eq_to_sumeq ([("Minion", 4400)]), to expression: (Sum([a, b, c, d, e]) = 5), resulting in: SumEq([a, b, c, d, e], 5)
Rule applicable: sumeq_to_minion ([("Minion", 4400)]), to expression: SumEq([a, b, c, d, e], 5), resulting in: And([SumGeq([a, b, c, d, e], 5), SumLeq([a, b, c, d, e], 5)])
